 DemoGridEmployees connected;F;Surname;JobTitle;Region;Salary;DATA;Jobs;Regions
 EWC.CONNECTED‚Üêconnected
 ‚éïPW‚Üê1000

‚çù The classic ‚éïWC Grid "Employee DataBase" example, ported to the EWC Grid
‚çù (‚éïWC ‚Üí eWC, property assignments ‚Üí eWS). Shown twice to contrast ShowInput:
‚çù   ‚Ä¢ top grid    ‚Äî ShowInput unset: Combo inputs appear only on the current cell
‚çù   ‚Ä¢ bottom grid ‚Äî ShowInput 1: Combo inputs are shown in every row

 F‚Üê'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'Employee DataBase'(50 50)(320 445)('Coord' 'Pixel')

 Surname‚Üê'Brown' 'Jones' 'Green' 'Black' 'White'
 JobTitle‚Üê'Manager' 'Project Leader' 'Consultant'
 JobTitle,‚Üê'Programmer' 'Assistant'
 Region‚Üê'South' 'South' 'South' 'East' 'Central'
 Salary‚Üê64000 43250 45000 30000 4000
 DATA‚Üê‚Üë[0.5]Surname JobTitle Region Salary
 Jobs‚ÜêJobTitle
 Regions‚Üê'North' 'South' 'East' 'West' 'Central'

‚çù ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ Grid 1: ShowInput unset ‚Äî inputs appear only on the current cell ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
 (F,'.LBL1')eWC'Label' 'ShowInput unset ‚Äî inputs appear on the current cell'(48 10)(18 420)
 (F,'.G')eWC'Grid'('Values' DATA)('Posn'(70 10))('Size'(102 403))
 (F,'.G.JobTitle')eWC'Combo'('Items' Jobs)
 (F,'.G.Region')eWC'Combo'('Items' Regions)
 (F,'.G.Salary')eWC'Label'('FieldType' 'Currency')
 (F,'.G')eWS'Input'('' (F,'.G.JobTitle')(F,'.G.Region')(F,'.G.Salary'))
 (F,'.G')eWS'CellTypes'((‚ç¥DATA)‚ç¥1 2 3 4)
 (F,'.G')eWS'TitleWidth' 0
 (F,'.G')eWS'ColTitles'('Surname' 'Job Title' 'Region' 'Salary')

‚çù ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ Grid 2: identical, but ShowInput 1 ‚Äî Combo inputs shown in every row ‚îÄ‚îÄ‚îÄ
 (F,'.LBL2')eWC'Label' 'ShowInput 1 ‚Äî Combo inputs shown in every row'(184 10)(18 420)
 (F,'.G2')eWC'Grid'('Values' DATA)('Posn'(206 10))('Size'(102 403))
 (F,'.G2.JobTitle')eWC'Combo'('Items' Jobs)
 (F,'.G2.Region')eWC'Combo'('Items' Regions)
 (F,'.G2.Salary')eWC'Label'('FieldType' 'Currency')
 (F,'.G2')eWS'Input'('' (F,'.G2.JobTitle')(F,'.G2.Region')(F,'.G2.Salary'))
 (F,'.G2')eWS'CellTypes'((‚ç¥DATA)‚ç¥1 2 3 4)
 (F,'.G2')eWS'TitleWidth' 0
 (F,'.G2')eWS'ColTitles'('Surname' 'Job Title' 'Region' 'Salary')
 (F,'.G2')eWS'ShowInput' 1
